Email-to-Case’s on-demand service keeps email traffic outside your network’s firewall and refuses emails that are too large.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Salesforce Classic, Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, Developer Editions

LIMIT	VALUE
The maximum number of emails processed daily: 1,000,000
10,000 email messages per day (users x 1,000)

Maximum size of inbound emails:
Inbound attachment size: up to 25 MB
Outbound email size: 384 KB

Maximum email length:
Email headers: 32,000 characters
Email body text: 131,072 characters

Inbound Email Size Limits
Attachment size and total email size: 35 MB
